Change log of WeKNotes. For more information see the HISTORY file.

0.3019 - Initial public release

0.3051 - Change authentication access to all be in one cgi script.

0.3055 - Documentation update

0.3055 - minor changes

0.3075 - 
Simplified config files.
rewrote wkn_index.
created example dir structure.

0.3077 - 
Added ability to delete note.
Added System acces user flag.
Enhanced userinfo for users with system access.
Fixed disappearing password.


0.3081 - bug fixes
            fixed/updated search.cgi

0.3082 - Files in dir go in separate table.

0.3095 - bug fixes. Added wkn_list.

0.3104 - Bug fixes. wkn_tables.cgi changes.

0.3123 - added .group, .permissions, and default permissions support

0.3137 - small script cleanup.

0.3141 - Updated INSTALL documentation.

0.3158 - fixed sessions dir

0.4001 - New more consistent configuration variable names. Added default icons def.

0.4051 - changed search.cgi to ignore unauthorized matches

0.5000 - Put all wkn methods and defines in wkn package.
Put all auth methods and defines in auth package.
use strict on all .cgi scripts.
moved color definitions into one file: wkn_attr.pl.
Simplification of define files.


0.5003 - Support for remote auth users(AUTH_TYPE, REMOTE_USER)
          - AUTH_USER fixes. sperl_user.c fixes

0.5004 - wkn::define::filename_filter fix

0.5008 - Added permissions.cgi.
Corrected file filter code.
Added edit_group.cgi.

0.5058 - list/frames stuff -incomplete

0.5107 - Frames list updates.
Bug Fixes.
Added cgitohtml (for home pages). Removed wkn_index.cgi (old home page method).

0.5123 - 
New frame/java script front (slower than expected).
Bug fixes ...
Cleanup ...

0.5130 - 
Added icon and icon_text definitions to define file.
Simplified sample wkn_define_sample file

0.600 -
First sourceforge version
CODE section filtering 
replaced file area notion with generic notes
external web path filter 
bug fixes 


0.6.08 - minor bug fix

0.7.0 -
-Restructured for simplification.
-'auth' and 'wkn' cgi directories merged, and now toplevel is same for
both.
-Lots of configuration definitions disappeared as a result.
-New 'configure' script to do a simple guess at setting up webknotes.
-New extendable user and group file format.(Requires conversion of old
files using util/ufile_convert)
-New more straightforware permissions scheme.
-New browse method that allows editing a directory. (This allows editing
and deleting non-note files)
-New uploade script to allow uploading none-note or binary items(if user
has 'u' permission in dir).

0.8.x -
This version removes all the attribute definition and instead uses 
CSS to define the look.
You can change your "theme" on the fly. 
Sample themes included.

0.9.x -
-pluggable file filters, 
-wiki support,
-mod_perl support
-css browser hacks. 
-auto back loading

0.A.x
-cvs client support
-file access is now nearly all done via filedb_lib
-files are locked for write and append
-subscription turned back on (subscription is still manual)
-new configure script that remembers your previous configuration (exept filters)
-verify email mechanism
